data.description: Great starter or downsizing home. Everything all on 1 floor. Large living room that opens up to the kitchen. Sun porch overlooks fenced in yard. New vinyl planking in kitchen last month. New vinyl planking in LR and carpet in bedrooms and hallway in 2021. New vanity and toilet in bath in 2022. Freshly resurfaced kitchen cabinets last month. Driveway recently widened to give you more room. Pull down attic for more storage.
